The ANC elective conference 2017 results is what everyone is looking forward to as ANC delegates are set to decide who will take the ANC forward. Tension characterized early events of this 2017 elective conference but the ANC was able to manage delegates anxiety. President Zuma delivered his political report which caught many by surprise as he made admission to some ANC failures. Many have described Zumaâ€™s report as his attempt to write his own legacy before the general public does so. Just before the ANC elective conference got underway, President Zuma surprised many when he announced that free education will be rolled out in 2018. Images posted by delegates and official ANC Facebook page showed both camps singing and chanting songs, a move which was a display of unity.    comments